HEADWORD: Morgay
<hw>Mor"gay</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[W. <ets>morgi</ets>
dogfish, shark; <ets>mor</ets> sea + <ets>ci</ets> dog.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>The European small-spotted dogfish, or
houndfish. See the Note under <er>Houndfish</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

